1. Intilized go module because golang use module for dependcies.
Yes, .proto files are case-sensitive.
Need to use this command (go run *.go) to run the client or server
In gRPC, the server chooses the port, and the client must be told which port to connect to.

# Role	   Who writes the method?	     Why?
Server	You write the method	You provide the actual business logic
Client	  Autogenerated for you	  Because gRPC knows how to call server      via network

in method 
.For unary RPCs, you return the response and error.
.For streaming RPCs, you use the stream parameter to send multiple responses and only return an error.